<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/10/21361545/folding-e-ink-reader-prototype-note-taking">E-Ink 展示可折叠电子墨水屏阅读器原型机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357695" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/flexible_e_ink_reader.gif" alt="" width="800" height="444" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/flexible_e_ink_reader.gif 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/flexible_e_ink_reader-360x200.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/flexible_e_ink_reader-768x426.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，E-Ink 展示了最新的可折叠电子墨水屏阅读器原型机。和此前版本相比，新版本采用了更坚固的铰链，设置了五个专用按钮和两个位于屏幕顶部的照明灯条，并集成了 Wacom 技术，用于记笔记，做批注等。</p>
